<h1 class="title-article">&nbsp;</h1>
<h1 class="title-article"><strong>在MySQL登录时出现Access denied for user 'root'@'localhost' (using password: YES) 拒绝访问，并可修改MySQL密码</strong></h1>
</div>
<div class="article-info-box">
<div class="article-bar-top"><strong><span class="time"><span class="time">2018年08月03日 09:51:36&nbsp;<a class="follow-nickName" href="https://me.csdn.net/qq_36675754" target="_blank">嘉禾-BILI</a>&nbsp;<span class="read-count">阅读数：17940&nbsp;<span class="tags-box artic-tag-box"><span class="label">标签：&nbsp;<a class="tag-link" href="http://so.csdn.net/so/search/s.do?q=MySQL%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AEroot%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7&amp;t=blog" target="_blank" data-track-click="{&quot;mod&quot;:&quot;popu_626&quot;,&quot;con&quot;:&quot;MySQL拒绝访问root用户&quot;}">MySQL拒绝访问root用户</a><span class="article_info_click">更多</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>
<div class="tags-box space"><strong><span class="label">个人分类：&nbsp;<a class="tag-link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36675754/article/category/7902486" target="_blank">MySQL</a></span></strong></div>
</div>
